\">161</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n<b>Year 298 After the Conquest</b> (<b>298 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 298th after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> which maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>298 AC sees the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a>, who had been <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> for fifteen years. King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a> entrusts the post to his childhood friend, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, and betrothes his heir, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a>, to Eddard's eldest daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>. After Robert dies from a hunting accident, Eddard declares that Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a>'s children are actually <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastards</a> and cannot inherit the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>. Eddard <a href=\"/index.php/Arrest_of_Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Arrest of Eddard Stark\">is arrested</a> and Joffrey is crowned. Several nobles oppose the new king in open revolt, setting the stage of the conflict that would be known as the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.\n</p><p>Many chapters from <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> take place during 298 AC.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Births\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Births</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Marriages\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Marriages</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Titles_and_Positions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Titles and Positions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=298_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><b>Conflicts</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth\">Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Mummer%27s_Ford\" title=\"Battle at the Mummer&#39;s Ford\">Battle at the Mummer's Ford</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Battle under the walls of Riverrun\">Battle under the walls of Riverrun</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Fall of Raventree Hall\">Fall of Raventree Hall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yielding_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Yielding of Harrenhal\">Yielding of Harrenhal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Pinkmaiden_Castle\" title=\"Burning of Pinkmaiden Castle\">Burning of Pinkmaiden Castle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Burning of Stone Hedge\">Burning of Stone Hedge</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Darry\" title=\"Capture of Darry\">Capture of Darry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/First_sack_of_Maidenpool\" title=\"First sack of Maidenpool\">First sack of Maidenpool</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>Other Events</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_on_Prince_Joffrey%27s_name_day\" title=\"Tourney on Prince Joffrey&#39;s name day\">Tourney on Prince Joffrey's name day</a> takes place in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a> leaves <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Water_Gardens\" title=\"Water Gardens\">Water Gardens</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Hand%27s_tourney\" title=\"Hand&#39;s tourney\">Hand's tourney</a> is held in honor of the appointment of Eddard Stark</li>\n<li>Following his loss at the tourney, <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> and his men gang-rape <a href=\"/index.php/Layna\" title=\"Layna\">Layna</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arrest_of_Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Arrest of Eddard Stark\">Arrest of Eddard Stark</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Births\">Births</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=298_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Births\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Six <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolves</a>, born near <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, are adopted by the children of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> after the pups are discovered near their dead mother<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Wind\" title=\"Grey Wind\">Grey Wind</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_(direwolf)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady (direwolf)\">Lady</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria_(direwolf)\" title=\"Nymeria (direwolf)\">Nymeria</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Summer_(direwolf)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Summer (direwolf)\">Summer</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shaggydog\" title=\"Shaggydog\">Shaggydog</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barra\" title=\"Barra\">Barra</a>, one of the many bastard children of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ermesande_Hayford\" title=\"Ermesande Hayford\">Ermesande Hayford</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Stone\" title=\"Alys Stone\">Alys Stone</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-twow_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-twow-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=298_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><b>In the North</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gared\" title=\"Gared\">Gared</a>, executed by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> for desertion from the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hali\" title=\"Hali\">Hali</a>, slain while trying to capture <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolfswood\" title=\"Wolfswood\">wolfswood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stiv\" title=\"Stiv\">Stiv</a>, slain in the wolfswood</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wallen\" title=\"Wallen\">Wallen</a>, slain in the wolfswood</li></ul>\n<p><b>At the Wall and Beyond</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jafer_Flowers\" title=\"Jafer Flowers\">Jafer Flowers</a>, slain <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Othor\" title=\"Othor\">Othor</a>, slain beyond the Wall</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaremy_Rykker\" title=\"Jaremy Rykker\">Jaremy Rykker</a>, slain by the <a href=\"/index.php/Wight\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wight\">wight</a> of Jafer at <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>Across the narrow sea</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Fogo\" title=\"Fogo\">Fogo</a>, slain near a <a href=\"/index.php/Lhazareen\" title=\"Lhazareen\">Lhazareen</a> settlement</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ogo\" title=\"Ogo\">Ogo</a>, slain near a Lhazareen settlement</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, killed when Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> pours molten gold over his head<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>In King's landing</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a>, poisoned with the <a href=\"/index.php/Tears_of_Lys\" title=\"Tears of Lys\">tears of Lys</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a>, wounded by a wild <a href=\"/index.php/Boar\" title=\"Boar\">boar</a> while hunting and dies from his wounds<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barra\" title=\"Barra\">Barra</a>, slain at <a href=\"/index.php/Chataya%27s_brothel\" title=\"Chataya&#39;s brothel\">Chataya's brothel</a> in King's Landing by <a href=\"/index.php/Allar_Deem\" title=\"Allar Deem\">Allar Deem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barra%27s_mother\" title=\"Barra&#39;s mother\">Barra's mother</a>, slain at Chataya's by Allar</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jory_Cassel\" title=\"Jory Cassel\">Jory Cassel</a>, slain by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister_guards\" title=\"House Lannister guards\">red cloaks</a> in the streets of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cayn\" title=\"Cayn\">Cayn</a>, slain in the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Hall_(Red_Keep)\" title=\"Great Hall (Red Keep)\">throne room</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Desmond\" title=\"Desmond\">Desmond</a>, slain in the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_the_Hand\" title=\"Tower of the Hand\">Tower of the Hand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Heward\" title=\"Heward\">Heward</a>, slain by red cloaks in the streets of King's Landing<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hugh\">Hugh of the Vale</a>, killed in the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand%27s_tourney\" title=\"Hand&#39;s tourney\">Hand's tourney</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hullen\" title=\"Hullen\">Hullen</a>, slain in the Tower of the Hand</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mordane\" title=\"Mordane\">Mordane</a>, slain in the Tower of the Hand</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vayon_Poole\" title=\"Vayon Poole\">Vayon Poole</a>, slain in the Tower of the Hand</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tomard\" title=\"Tomard\">Tomard</a>, slain in the throne room of the Red Keep</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tregar\" title=\"Tregar\">Tregar</a>, dies of wounds suffered in the streets of King's Landing</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Varly\" title=\"Varly\">Varly</a>, slain in the throne room of the Red Keep</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wyl_(guard)\" title=\"Wyl (guard)\">Wyl</a>, slain by red cloaks in the streets of King's Landing<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>In the Riverlands</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Raymun_Darry\" title=\"Raymun Darry\">Raymun Darry</a>, slain during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Mummer%27s_Ford\" title=\"Battle at the Mummer&#39;s Ford\">battle at the Mummer's Ford</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_(direwolf)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady (direwolf)\">Lady</a>, killed by <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Darry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lorimer_the_Belly\" title=\"Lorimer the Belly\">Lorimer the Belly</a>, hanged for stealing</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cedric_Payne\" title=\"Cedric Payne\">Cedric Payne</a>, dies fighting in the riverlands</li></ul>\n<p><b>In the Vale of Arryn</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Chiggen\" title=\"Chiggen\">Chiggen</a>, slain in the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vardis_Egen\" title=\"Vardis Egen\">Vardis Egen</a>, slain during a trial by combat at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jyck\" title=\"Jyck\">Jyck</a>, slain in the Mountains of the Moon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kurleket\" title=\"Kurleket\">Kurleket</a>, slain in the Mountains of the Moon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lharys\" title=\"Lharys\">Lharys</a>, slain in the Mountains of the Moon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mohor\" title=\"Mohor\">Mohor</a>, slain in the Mountains of the Moon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Morrec\" title=\"Morrec\">Morrec</a>, slain in the Mountains of the Moon</li></ul>\n<p><b>In the Westerlands</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Vance\" title=\"Lord Vance\">Lord Vance</a>, the father of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Karyl_Vance\" title=\"Karyl Vance\">Karyl Vance</a>, slain at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth\">battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Marriages\">Marriages</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=298_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Marriages\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Drogo_and_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Wedding of Drogo and Daenerys Targaryen\">The wedding</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Walder_Frey_and_Joyeuse_Erenford\" title=\"Wedding of Walder Frey and Joyeuse Erenford\">The wedding</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Joyeuse_Erenford\" title=\"Joyeuse Erenford\">Joyeuse Erenford</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Titles_and_Positions\">Titles and Positions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=298_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Titles and Positions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><b>King</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a> is crowned</li></ul>\n<p><b>Small Council</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> to King Joffrey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a> is named the <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Queen Regent</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Janos_Slynt\" title=\"Janos Slynt\">Janos Slynt</a> joins the council as an advisor</li></ul>\n<p><b>Lord</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Karyl_Vance\" title=\"Karyl Vance\">Karyl Vance</a> inherits the title of <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"Lord of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">Lord of Wayfarer's Rest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Janos_Slynt\" title=\"Janos Slynt\">Janos Slynt</a> is raised to <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Lord of Harrenhal\">Lord of Harrenhal</a>, establishing <a href=\"/index.php/House_Slynt\" title=\"House Slynt\">House Slynt</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>Kingsguard</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> is removed from the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> is named new <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> is made a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>, despite the fact he is not a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>Castellan</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>Other Titles</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> is made a <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khaleesi\" title=\"Khaleesi\">khaleesi</a></i> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Willamen_Frey\" title=\"Willamen Frey\">Willamen Frey</a> takes his vows and becomes a maester</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=298_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, Catelyn IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc2.7B